The Rivers chapter of All Progressives Congress (APC) says it has suspended the planned Ward, Local Government and State congresses in the state due to development in the judiciary. <img class="alignnone wp-image-1248681" src="https://i1.wp.com/cdn.vanguardngr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/APC.png?resize=353%2C353&#038;ssl=1" alt="APC" width="353" height="353" srcset="https://i1.wp.com/cdn.vanguardngr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/APC.png?resize=300%2C300&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i1.wp.com/cdn.vanguardngr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/APC.png?resize=107%2C107&amp;ssl=1 107w, https://i1.wp.com/cdn.vanguardngr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/APC.png?resize=58%2C58&amp;ssl=1 58w, https://i1.wp.com/cdn.vanguardngr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/APC.png?resize=194%2C194&amp;ssl=1 194w, https://i1.wp.com/cdn.vanguardngr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/APC.png?resize=130%2C130&amp;ssl=1 130w, https://i1.wp.com/cdn.vanguardngr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/APC.png?w=550&amp;ssl=1 550w" sizes="(max-width: 353px) 100vw, 353px" data-recalc-dims="1" /> Mr Isaac Ogbobula, the state’s caretaker committee chairman of the party, disclosed this while speaking with newsmen at the party’s secretariat in Port Harcourt on Monday, NAN reported. “The planned congresses of APC in Rivers has been put on hold as directed by the National Working Committee (NWC) of the party in view of the development in the Judiciary. “The NWC is responsible for the necessary reconciliation process,” he said. The Acting Chairman assured party faithful that all other party activities would go on unhindered in the state. Supporters of a former lawmaker, Sen. Magnus Abe had threatened to boycott the Congresses for not being consulted. Vanguard News. ALL Progressives Congress, APC, has suspended its planned Congresses for Rivers state billed to commence Tuesday. September 16, 2019 In "News" ABUJA—The National Working Committee, NWC, of All Progressives Congress, APC, has approved the appointment of Mr Yekini Nabena as acting National Publicity Secretary of the party. August 2, 2018 In "News" ABUJA - The national leadership of the All Progressives Congress APC has dissolved the Kwara state executive of the party, citing electoral malfeasance in the last ward, local and state congresses. July 30, 2018 In "News"